      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. yeah it's such a nightmare right now. the airport is just pure chaos w all these delays and people running around. i feel like the airline system is just totally breaking down. do u think i should just wait for them to rebook me or should i try to find my own flight through a different airline right now?",
